text: Dynamic preaching. Caring pastors. Good church to learn more about God

At Grace Assembly of God, we welcome your multi-generational family to make this your home church where you can worship together and be discipled to become more like Jesus.

We can help too, if you are seeking to find out more about God or the Christian faith.

Excellent Church! Good and warm fellowship - both in Chinese(Mandarin, Hokkien, Cantonese) and English. Conveniently located with sufficient car park all round. Near to many eating places including West Mall.
Went for a wedding, nice and cosy church with facilities needed. Accessible via buses and near mrt
Hi Friends, come, visit "Grace Assembly of God". It is a church welcome to everyone to visit, be you a believer or a non-believer. God loves and bless you always.
